v1.0.6, 9/9/2015

  * Added JSDoc comments.

  * Fixed URL construction where the Auth Provider base URL contains a path
    component.

  * Updated Gruntfile to fix 'test' task.

v1.0.5, 4/9/2015

  * Use URIjs module to construct URLs.

  * Updated Gruntfile to fix 'watch' task.

v1.0.4, 18/8/2015

  * Added contributors to bower.json and package.json.

v1.0.3, 10/12/2014

  * Replaced QUnit with mocha test framework.

  * Use CommonJS-style modules and browserify instead of Require.js.

v1.0.2, 3/8/2014

  * Initial version. Corresponds with the Cross Platform Authentication
    protocol v1.0.

    See https://tech.ebu.ch/docs/tech/tech3366.pdf
